 must be created by the method and\nthe active record of the created payment record should be returned.\n\nA helper function is provided in this class itself which fills in most\nof the information automatically and the only additional information\nrequired is the reference from the payment provider.\n\nIf return_profile is set to True in the context, then the created\nprofile is returned."]}], "class_variables": [{"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.AddPaymentProfile.__name__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.AddPaymentProfile.start_state", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.AddPaymentProfile.card_info", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.AddPaymentProfile.add", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Add a payment profile"]}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.TransactionUseCardView", "bases": ["BaseCreditCardViewMixin", "ModelView"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.TransactionUseCardView.__name__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["View for putting in credit card information"]}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.TransactionUseCard", "bases": ["Wizard"], "methods": [{"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.TransactionUseCard.transition_capture", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Delegates to the capture method for the provider in\npayment_gateway.transaction"]}, {"name": "trytond.modules.payment_gateway.transaction.TransactionUseCard.transition_authorize", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "docum